data.description: Lovely single story home with 4 bedrooms  and 2 baths looking for a new owner.   Large kitchen with an abundance of cabinets and breakfast bar.   Living room with wood burning stove.   Main bedroom with en-suite with separate tub and shower and large walk in closet.   Beautiful fenced backyard with fire pit, cement pathways and even a greenhouse. 21x23 covered Composite  patio .  9.5 kw solar system included.
